{"type":"text","timestamp":1775866029327,"sessionID":"ses_286289c44ffeoJBcO7yVHd6sSt","part":{"id":"prt_d79dcde3a001Trah2DHY2j63e0","messageID":"msg_d79dc91ee001jv9D8rDxJ2ZJOZ","sessionID":"ses_286289c44ffeoJBcO7yVHd6sSt","type":"text","text":"Based on my analysis, I found a **spec mismatch** and **compilation errors**. Let me provide a detailed verification report:\n\n## Verification Report: AR-012 — Session Storage Interface\n\n### 1. Spec Mismatch Detected\n\n**AR-012 spec** mentions:\n- Module: `pkg/store` — 会话存储接口定义 (Session Storage Interface Definition)\n- Language: Go, Size: S\n\n**However**, the spec content provided is for **`client-go` library** (Kubernetes client code), while the **actual implementation** in the workspace is the **`pkg/store`** module for session storage with Redis/Valkey backends.\n\n**Correct spec location**: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/session-store/spec.md`\n\n---\n\n### 2. Store Interface Implementation Verification\n\nThe `Store` interface in `pkg/store/store.go` **matches** the session-store spec requirements:\n\n| Spec Requirement | Implementation Status |\n|------------------|----------------------|\n| `Ping(ctx) error` | ✅ Implemented (redis.go:64, valkey.go:75) |\n| `GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)` | ✅ Implemented |\n| `StoreSandbox(ctx, sandbox) error` | ✅ Implemented with SETNX + ZADD atomic |\n| `UpdateSandbox(ctx, sandbox) error` | ✅ Implemented with SET XX |\n| `DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionID) error` | ✅ Implemented with DEL + ZREM |\n| `ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx, before, limit)` | ✅ Implemented with ZRANGEBYSCORE |\n| `ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx, before, limit)` | ✅ Implemented with ZRANGEBYSCORE |\n| `UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, sessionID, at)` | ✅ Implemented |\n| `Close() error` | ✅ Implemented |\n| `ErrNotFound` sentinel error | ✅ Defined (store.go:28) |\n| Singleton `Storage()` with `sync.Once` | ✅ Implemented (singleton.go:61) |\n\n---\n\n### 3. Compilation Errors Found ❌\n\nThe code has **6 compilation errors** that need to be fixed:\n\n```\npkg/store/redis.go:279:6: declared and not used: i\npkg/store/valkey.go:144:34: cannot use data ([]byte) as string value\npkg/store/valkey.go:191:57: cannot use data ([]byte) as string value  \npkg/store/valkey.go:249:34: zrangeResult.ToStringSlice undefined\npkg/store/valkey.go:272:34: zrangeResult.ToStringSlice undefined\npkg/store/valkey.go:299:29: mgetResult.ToStringSlice undefined\n```\n\n**Issues identified:**\n1. **Unused variable** in `redis.go` line 279 (loop variable `i` not used)\n2. **Type mismatch** in `valkey.go`: `[]byte` cannot be used as `string` for Valkey client\n3. **Missing method** `ToStringSlice()` - Valkey library uses different API\n\n---\n\n### 4. Test Status\n\n**No tests found** for `pkg/store` module. The spec requires test coverage but there are no `*_test.go` files in the store package.\n\n---\n\n### 5. Summary\n\n| Category | Status |\n|----------|--------|\n| Interface Definition | ✅ Matches spec |\n| Redis Implementation | ✅ Logic correct, but has compile error (unused var) |\n| Valkey Implementation | ⚠️ Has multiple compile errors (type mismatch, missing methods) |\n| Singleton Access | ✅ Correctly implemented |\n| Environment Configuration | ✅ Supports STORE_TYPE, Redis/Valkey env vars |\n| Tests | ❌ No tests present |\n\n**Recommendation**: The `pkg/store` implementation structurally matches the session-store spec requirements, but requires fixes for compilation errors before it can be used. The spec provided in the request appears to be mismatched with the actual implementation scope.","time":{"start":1775866029324,"end":1775866029324}}}
